<arggraph id="micro_c193" topic_id="treat_dogs_as_humans" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[It is OK to treat dogs on par with family members]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[because they're a part of the family.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[We look after them as we do our own family.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[We feed them, bath them, take them to their appointments.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[We want to make sure they're ok, like the ones we love.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[They also give us comfort and warm feelings and help promote a happier lifestyle.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[They're fulling and fun to be around.]]></edu>
